  "title": "Retail Loan Operation Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>1. Coordinating with Law firm on the checking and clarification of retail mortgage documentation.<br />2. Perform all aspects of disbursement, payments and redemption pertaining to Loan Processing.<br />3. Ensure compliance in safekeeping of all security and confidential documentations are strictly adhered.<br />4. Review and ensure all relevant conditions precedents are met before activation of credit facility.<br />5. Achieve or exceed given specific performance standards in both turnaround time and accuracy.<br />6. Performing general maintenance including data input, related report and preparation of legal profile.<br />7. Participate in all process improvement of system projects or enhancements.<br />8. Any ad-hoc tasks assigned.      </p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>1. Diploma and above<br />2. At least 1 years banking related experience in accounting, loan operations, or law firm preferred.<br />3. Proficiency n Microsoft Application (Excel and Word)<br />4. Good interpersonal and communication skills <br />5. Meticulous with an eye for details and quality mindset.6. Able to multi-task and work in a team as well as independently while under pressure to deliver with tight deadlines</p><p></p>",
